OL,3,CNHS Trust to pay out nearly #30
OL,4,Cmillion after baby 'catastrophically
OL,5,Cinjured'
OL,7,FThe family of a baby girl left with
OL,8,Fcatastrophic injuries after negligent
OL,9,Fcare will receive nearly #30 million
OL,10,Fin compensation - one of the biggest
OL,11,Fsettlements ever reached.
OL,13,FThe baby - who is the subject of an
OL,14,Fanonymity order - sustained
OL,15,Fcatastrophic and life-changing
OL,16,Finjuries in the form of cerebral palsy
OL,17,Fafter a series of negligent omissions
OL,18,Fin her post-natal care and a delay in
OL,19,Fhaving surgery.
