OL,3,CNHS Trust to pay out nearly #30
OL,4,Cmillion after baby 'catastrophically
OL,5,Cinjured'
OL,7,FThe payout is believed to be the
OL,8,Fsecond largest settlement in a medical
OL,9,Fnegligence claim against the NHS,
OL,10,Fafter Stockport NHS Foundation Trust
OL,11,Fadmitted full admission of liability.
OL,13,FThe payout of #29.3 million, was
OL,14,Fapproved at the High Court in London.
OL,16,FThe girl and her family were
OL,17,Frepresented by solicitor Yasmin Ameer
OL,18,Ffrom Nockolds Solicitors and
OL,19,Fbarristers Bill Braithwaite KC and
OL,20,FChris Allen from Exchange Chambers.
