OL,4,Cmillion after baby 'catastrophically
OL,5,Cinjured'
OL,7,FCommenting on the case, Bill
OL,8,FBraithwaite KC said: "This young
OL,9,Fgirl's life has changed forever and
OL,10,Fthe impact on the whole family has
OL,11,Fbeen devastating.
OL,13,F"They waited a number of years for
OL,14,FStockport NHS Foundation Trust to
OL,15,Fadmit liability and faced the prospect
OL,16,Fof a trial at court until we finally
OL,17,Freached a settlement. Justice has now
OL,18,Fbeen done and they can finally look to
OL,19,Fthe future knowing her lifelong needs
OL,20,Fare provided for."
