OL,7,FYasmin Ameer said: "This is a hugely
OL,8,Fimportant settlement for a young
OL,9,Fperson whose life has been
OL,10,Firreversibly damaged.
OL,12,F"Her whole family have shown such
OL,13,Fbravery and I pay tribute to them all.
OL,14,FIt has been an honour to represent
OL,15,Fthem."
OL,17,FStockport NHS Foundation Trust has
OL,18,Fbeen approached for comment.
